titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on lambdacyhalothrin.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 10/5/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1996, the duty on 1a(S),3a(Z))-(+)-cyano-(3-phenoxyphenyl)-methyl 3-(2-chloro-3, 3,3-trifluoro-1-propenyl)-2,2-dimethylcyclopropanecarboxylate (also known as lambdacyhalothrin).
